high_descs: Pick up the sponge on the left from the tub.
Bring the sponge to the sink.
Wet the sponge in the sink with water.
Bring the sponge to the metal rack.
Put the sponge on the top metal rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge on the metal rack.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the black mat next to the bath tub, and face the bath tub.
Grab the leftmost sponge in the bath tub.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Rinse the sponge in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the rack.
Place the sponge on the top rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a wet sponge on the rack.

high_descs: Go to the left and face the faucet side of the bath tub.
Pick up left most green sponge from the bath tub.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink. Turn on then turn off the water. Take the sponge from the sink.
Go to the metal bar rack to the left.
Put the sponge on the top rack to the left of the lotion bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on a metal rack.
